snippet.title: Cities: Skylines II - Pre-Order Trailer
snippet.description: If you can dream it, you can build it. Raise a city from nothing and grow it into a thriving metropolis with the most realistic city builder ever. This is world-building without limits. Cities: Skylines II will be available on PC, Gamepass, and Xbox Series X|S on October 24th. Pre-order to receive a bonus with landmarks from around the world!
